articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about the site
articles.contents: This site is meant to be a collection of informative resources that I read centered largely around Machine Learning. Material on this site is constantly being updated so most of the notes (especially coursework related) will be very incomplete. For a lot of articles (especially coursework related), there are PDFs that are attached as well (on the right side of the margin at the start of the article).
